      "set:html": "<div class=\"sl-heading-wrapper level-h2\"><h2 id=\"custom-markdoc-nodes--elements\">Custom Markdoc nodes / elements</h2><a class=\"sl-anchor-link\" href=\"#custom-markdoc-nodes--elements\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"sl-anchor-icon\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentcolor\" d=\"m12.11 15.39-3.88 3.88a2.52 2.52 0 0 1-3.5 0 2.47 2.47 0 0 1 0-3.5l3.88-3.88a1 1 0 0 0-1.42-1.42l-3.88 3.89a4.48 4.48 0 0 0 6.33 6.33l3.89-3.88a1 1 0 1 0-1.42-1.42Zm8.58-12.08a4.49 4.49 0 0 0-6.33 0l-3.89 3.88a1 1 0 0 0 1.42 1.42l3.88-3.88a2.52 2.52 0 0 1 3.5 0 2.47 2.47 0 0 1 0 3.5l-3.88 3.88a1 1 0 1 0 1.42 1.42l3.88-3.89a4.49 4.49 0 0 0 0-6.33ZM8.83 15.17a1 1 0 0 0 1.1.22 1 1 0 0 0 .32-.22l4.92-4.92a1 1 0 0 0-1.42-1.42l-4.92 4.92a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.42Z\"></path></svg></span><span class=\"sr-only\">Section titled ‚ÄúCustom Markdoc nodes / elements‚Äù</span></a></div>\n<p>You may want to render standard Markdown elements, such as paragraphs and bolded text, as Astro components. For this, you can configure a <a href=\"https://markdoc.dev/docs/nodes\">Markdoc node</a>. If a given node receives attributes, they will be available as component props.</p>\n<p>This example renders blockquotes with a custom <code dir=\"auto\">Quote.astro</code> component:</p>\n<div class=\"expressive-code\"><figure class=\"frame has-title not-content\"><figcaption class=\"header\"><span class=\"title\">markdoc.config.mjs</span></figcaption><pre data-language=\"js\"><code><div class=\"ec-line\"><div class=\"code\"><span style=\"--0:#C792EA;--1:#8844AE\">import</span><span style=\"--0:#D6DEEB;--1:#403F53\"> { defineMarkdocConfig, nodes, component } </span><span style=\"--0:#C792EA;--1:#8844AE\">from</span><span style=\"--0:#D6DEEB;--1:#403F53\"> </span><span style=\"--0:#D9F5DD;--1:#111111\">'</span><span style=\"--0:#ECC48D;--1:#984E4D\">@astrojs/markdoc/config</span><span style=\"--0:#D9F5DD;--1:#111111\">'</span><span style=\"--0:#D6DEEB;--1:#403F53\">;</span></div></div><div class=\"ec-line\"><div class=\"code\">\n</div></div><div class=\"ec-line\"><div class=\"code\"><span style=\"--0:#C792EA;--1:#8844AE\">export</span><span style=\"--0:#D6DEEB;--1:#403F53\"> </span><span style=\"--0:#C792EA;--1:#8844AE\">default</span><span style=\"--0:#D6DEEB;--1:#403F53\"> </span><span style=\"--0:#82AAFF;--1:#3B61B0\">defineMarkdocConfig</span><span style=\"--0:#D6DEEB;--1:#403F53\">({</span></div></div><div class=\"ec-line\"><div class=\"code\"><span class=\"indent\"><span style=\"--0:#D6DEEB;--1:#403F53\">  </span></span><span style=\"--0:#D6DEEB;--1:#403F53\">nodes: {</span></div></div><div class=\"ec-line\"><div class=\"code\"><span class=\"indent\"><span style=\"--0:#D6DEEB;--1:#403F53\">    </span></span><span style=\"--0:#D6DEEB;--1:#403F53\">blockquote: {</span></div></div><div class=\"ec-line\"><div class=\"code\"><span class=\"indent\">      </span><span style=\"--0:#7FDBCA;--1:#096E72\">...nodes</span><span style=\"--0:#C792EA;--1:#8844AE\">.</span><span style=\"--0:#7FDBCA;--1:#096E72\">blockquote</span><span style=\"--0:#D6DEEB;--1:#403F53\">, </span><span style=\"--0:#919F9F;--1:#5D6376\">// Apply Markdoc's defaults for other options</span></div></div><div class=\"ec-line\"><div class=\"code\"><span class=\"indent\"><span style=\"--0:#D6DEEB;--1:#403F53\">      </span></span><span style=\"--0:#D6DEEB;--1:#403F53\">render: </span><span style=\"--0:#82AAFF;--1:#3B61B0\">component</span><span style=\"--0:#D6DEEB;--1:#403F53\">(</span><span style=\"--0:#D9F5DD;--1:#111111\">'</span><span style=\"--0:#ECC48D;--1:#984E4D\">./src/components/Quote.astro</span><span style=\"--0:#D9F5DD;--1:#111111\">'</span><span style=\"--0:#D6DEEB;--1:#403F53\">),</span></div></div><div class=\"ec-line\"><div class=\"code\"><span class=\"indent\"><span style=\"--0:#D6DEEB;--1:#403F53\">    </span></span><span style=\"--0:#D6DEEB;--1:#403F53\">},</span></div></div><div class=\"ec-line\"><div class=\"code\"><span class=\"indent\"><span style=\"--0:#D6DEEB;--1:#403F53\">  </span></span><span style=\"--0:#D6DEEB;--1:#403F53\">},</span></div></div><div class=\"ec-line\"><div class=\"code\"><span style=\"--0:#D6DEEB;--1:#403F53\">});</span></div></div></code></pre><div class=\"copy\"><button title=\"Copy to clipboard\" data-copied=\"Copied!\" data-code=\"import { defineMarkdocConfig, nodes, component } from &#x27;@astrojs/markdoc/config&#x27;;export default defineMarkdocConfig({  nodes: {    blockquote: {      ...nodes.blockquote, // Apply Markdoc&#x27;s defaults for other options      render: component(&#x27;./src/components/Quote.astro&#x27;),    },  },});\"><div></div></button></div></figure></div>\n"
